---
title: One Pot Beef and Pork Penne with "Hidden" Zucchini and Carrots
description: This quick and easy meal comes together in one pot! It's especially good for choosy eaters, because we've hidden lots of wholesome veggies in the savoury sauce. They won't even know they're in there!
